{"tid":1519843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"831唔係end game","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:14:22.000Z","uid":175580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"252455f4d077529e976876b9d5000694e95ed00c","tid":1519843,"uid":175580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔知點解無啦啦有風向話聽日係最後一戰<br />\n聽日唔係最後呀！<br />\n我地仲有排打架 五大訴求一個都未訴求到呀<br />\n我地仲有9月1，2和你飛<br />\n呢埸戰爭係長期架 <br />\n唔好抱住聽日最後一戰就豁曬出去嘅心態 <br />\n我地未贏  要鬥長命<br />\n十月一仲要送份大禮比國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足聽日見  齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日唔係唔係唔係end game</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"42ae26dd161c19b5c677dc79bdef60f7bffb5dcd","tid":1519843,"uid":175580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57ba6437fce7c6219622ed05cc00ae678606a920","tid":1519843,"uid":175580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"831唔係end game"},{"pid":"814997ec0de6628278c5a48c4d7f80ab1e7ba5bc","tid":1519843,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/5nobb2zmllj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F5nobb2zmllj31.jpg&h=7e932cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.re